name: Quiz Activity Lacking Info
query:
SELECT `tabQuiz Activity`.name as "Activity Code",
`tabQuiz Activity`.quiz_title as "Quiz Title",
`tabQuiz Activity`.student_name as "Student Name",
DATE(`tabQuiz Activity`.activity_date) as "Activity Date",
`tabQuiz Activity`.course as "Subject",
`tabQuiz Activity`.program as "Program",
`tabQuiz Activity`.topic as "Topic",
`tabQuiz Activity`.quarter as "Quarter"
 FROM `tabQuiz Activity` WHERE `tabQuiz Activity`.topic='' OR `tabQuiz Activity`.program='' OR `tabQuiz Activity`.quarter='' 
 OR `tabQuiz Activity`.student_name='' ORDER BY `tabQuiz Activity`.quiz_title
